<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l1">VVir dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc
                                <expan>Bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> etc Als die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l2"><expan>hernachgeſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> ~
                                <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>kauffleute<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l3">etvvieuil irer habe vnd
                            <expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l4">vnd genomen heten . die ſie Jn
                                <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l5">vnd gekert <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . daran die
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein genüge
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l6">Als ſıe vns geſagt vnd auch gebeten
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l9">daʒ vvir darümb <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dıe
                        das <add><ab facs="#facs_509_line_1592200255515_1394">alſo </ab></add> getan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l10">freund <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> wolten . Vnd
                        Alſo vverden vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l11">
<expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> aller <del rend="strikethrough">dıe </del>
<expan>mıtname<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Heincʒe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Gocʒe<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l12">vnd <expan>dyecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> alle drey von
                        wolferſtorff Nykel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l13">Vorſters Steffans von Schönfelt knehte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l14">Thomas von der Rüche <expan>H<ex>eincʒ</ex></expan> .
                        Schonvvenrads . <expan>h<ex>eincʒ</ex></expan> vom </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_r1l15">liehtenſtein hanſen witlenders hanſen Schöteners </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_509_line_1593155741788_277"><expan cert="unknown">h</expan>  .
